                        <p><i class="fas fa-phone me-2"></i> (555) 987-6543</p>
                        <p><i class="fas fa-clock me-2"></i> Open today: 9am - 5pm</p>
                        <button class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm mt-2">Schedule Appointment</button>
